It‚Äôs been one hell of a week!
Battled malaria from Sunday to Thursday, chased thief that entered our compound this morning. 
Now this? No now üò´üò≠üò≠üò≠

People on here will say, "Hard time concentrating today. I had a fever and flu-like stuff. You know, headaches, chills, vomiting, nausea. My jaundice is worse. Really not helping that there are all these mosquitoes around. ü´§ ADHD symptoms kicking my ass!"

YOU HAVE MALARIA.
My experience of malaria was just taking anti-malarials, which give you strange dreams, because I don't want to get malaria.
I cannot talk about the benefits of eggs, garlic, ginger, Tumeric and water enough, I've only taken drugs ONCE since this year and it was to treat Malaria, a very big win and improvement for me.
